RACE.FOOTNOTES: LASSIE MY GIRL forwardly placed and inside, continued within striking distance turn, moved out three wide turning for home, engaged the leader inside the furlong marker and wore that foe down. MS CARROLL COUNTY off the pace while racing outside, made a strong move four down to three wide to take over through the turn, clear a furlong out, gave ground grudgingly to the winner, clearly second best. UNCLE SHORTYS GIRL settled off the pace along the inside, steadied early turn, mild rally to finish up best of the rest. KOKOMO STARLET away well, set the early pace in the two path, relinquished the advantage to the runner up midway on the turn and began to gradually weaken. BE BO in mid pack in the run up the backstretch, dropped inside late in the turn, went evenly through the lane. DELTA MOON fractious in the gate, three wide through the turn, continued one paced through the stretch in lacking a closing response. TIZ A STRATEGY fell back quickly to trail after the start, improved position while three to four wide into the stretch, failed to sustain that advance in the late going. QUEENIES WAY in the second flight off the inside, tired in the drive. MAY DISCO broke back, three out to four wide through the turn, made little impact through the lane. ONLYTHREESOCKS off a step slow, raced off the pace and the inside, was not a factor. MO WANNA GO forwardly placed while three wide early, began a steady retreat before a half. ALTAR GIRL was always outrun, trailed home.
